
### Get all contacts
GET http://localhost:8080/contacts

### Get one contact
GET http://localhost:8080/contacts/69b085f384a12eafeb642743

### Create new contact
POST http://localhost:8080/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Gianna",
    "lastName": "Garcia",
    "email": "gigi@sample.edu",
    "favoriteColor": "Pink",
    "birthday": "04/29"
  }

### Update contact
PUT http://localhost:8080/contacts/69b085f384a12eafeb642743 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type:  application/json

{
    "_id": "69b0f8ee84a12eafeb64274d",
    "firstName": "Justin",
    "lastName": "Snow",
    "email": "snowjnew@sample.com",
    "favoriteColor": "Gray",
    "birthday": "05/06"
  }

### Delete contact
DELETE http://localhost:8080/contacts/69b0f6df84a12eafeb642747

